Bonita has only been on deviantART since February 2010, yet thanks to her shitty fanart and propensity for leaving a trail of [[Tubgirl|verbal diarrhea,]] she has already attracted a small army of [[fags|friends]] who are nearly as retarded as she is. If you mention how lame her [[otherkin|deluded fantasy]] is, you can expect her [[retard|autopals]] to call you out on it. This has led to [http://comments.deviantart.com/5/31343391/1437124443 some lulzy threads, especially when Bonita forgets to hide the comments]. 

