== She's not really a truck driver ==

[[File:Mrsophascrabs.jpg|thumb|300px|left|These crabs were rescued from Bonita's bionic [[bush]].]]
[[File:Mrsbonitaoneprimeandtruck.jpg|thumb|Bonita Prime sitting on the step a Peterbilt Truck. It belongs to Blue Ridge Community College. She doesn't own it.]]

She states in her page bio that she's a truck driver before her [[lie|accident]] which turned her into [[Transformer|Robonita.]] We seriously doubt she really knows what a truck driver [[masturbation|does]] [[Lolicon|when]] [[Shotacon|they're]] [[Pedophilia|out]] [[Jailbait|on]] [[Rape|the]] [[Rule 34|road]].

[[File:Anotherbonitiablankstare.jpg|thumb|Here she is with a shark stare - with the dead eyes and the dead look appearance.]]

[[File:Mybullshitlicenseupdated.JPG|thumb|Here is my updated CDL with my new legal name and my real home address on it, with an old copy of my CDL with my birthdate whited out and real address. I didn't get permission from Hasbro, didn't need to he's my husband.]]

[[Some argue|She claimed]] that she was on vacation from being a [[bullshit|truck driver]] [[last Thursday|on August 27, 2010]], that her two weeks were now up, and she went back on the road. She recently posted photos of her sitting on the seat of "her" [[Optimus Prime|Peterbilt]] truck, which she claims to have bought used with her welfare money. Bonita had told another DA member that she was [[lies|totally broke]]. Bonita guessed it was time to restart her greatest lie of them all - going back on the road as a trucker.

She [[fail|magically appeared online]] during the time she claimed she was on the road to post on several people's comment boards. She must have one sticky keyboard full of tuna cum and doughnut crumbs. Truth is [[fact|truckers are not able to get online until they reach home base or have an extended wait time to unload, which is uncommon]], and yet she was able to be on every day at every hour, except this past week. She posted several comments to her friends and watchers, which means [[your argument is invalid|she's not a trucker.]]. She claims that she owns a Peterbilt [[Xbox|360]] - a very rare truck that is not seen beyond [[Tiger's Wood|the lumber yards]] as they were made in the 1950's. By the look of the truck she's posing with it would be rather expensive to run and maintain it's condition for it to be roadworthy. She must have a [[pimp|rich sponsor]] to supply her with funds to keep it up and running and plus to watch over her robotic [[lie|son]].

She [[wat|states that she's an East Coast trucker]], which is more [[bullshit]]. If she was, her son would be in a foster home as his mother is [[batshit insane|not able to care for him]]; however, it is now known she had lost custody of her so-called son to her shoplifting teacher of a mother.

A call to the Blue Ridge Community College, in Weyers Cave, VA, revealed that Bonita was a student there but she [[fact|does not own the truck pictured on her DA page.]] The truck that she claims is hers is the college's truck the students train in. Bonita is trying to purchase the truck with the help of the [[faggot|semi instructor]] who taught her how to drive it. Unlikely, as semi instructors wouldn't be concerned about what the students did after they finished their course, especially one they found molesting the school truck on a semi-regular basis. Get it? [[BAHDUM TISH|Semi-regular?]]

Robonita is currently unemployed, proven in her being [[basement dweller|online for hours]]. Her diarrhea trail rolls from [[Facebook]] to [[deviantART]] to her [[blog]]. She stated before that no one is with her in her cab as she's on the road, [[lolwut|which allows her to be able to be online without her boss being concerned.]] She admitted on her DA account that she is a trained semi driver but she is not driving a semi at this moment, and is most likely hustling Johns for money to buy all her Transformers figures, or else she continues to shoplift them.

