== Her Art ==
[[Image:Optimusfuckingcolored.jpg|thumb|[http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mechaphilia Her lunacy is most fully illustrated here, as her 30-foot cyborg incarnation of herself is anally violated by a fictional robot, while her BFF watches and faps to the display.]]]
Bonita claims to have gone to [[art school|art school]], which is clearly bullshit considering her art looks like it was drawn by an [[asspie|autistic twelve-year-old.]] Most of her masterpieces feature Bonita in different poses, usually hanging off Optimus Prime who is typically just sitting there like [http://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DullSurprise a dumbfuck with robodowns.] When the time comes to color, she uses the [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Crayons finest tools at her disposal.] Along with her beloved Optimus she likes to draw a Peterbilt truck, always at the same angle, which she has drawn [[at least 100]] times.

In her art, Bonita depicts herself as some kind of half human, half robot monstrosity in a white minidress [[hardcore|with flames on it]]. She has trouble deciding which parts of her are robotic and which aren't, most commonly her eyes. Her most recent drawing exploits her [[Mary Sue]] self having [[anal]] sex with Optimus while her BFF “Fritos” looks on, presumably envious.

Most of the shit screencapped here was removed by the moderators of DeviantART, although Robo-nita claims otherwise. Hammered for being a [[trace]] artist, she's [[shit]]ting herself now that we all know the hideous truth. 

