== Bonita the Stalker, the Copycat and [[haxxor|her attempt at trying to removing a fan's Autobot website]] ==

For months, Bonita has had an obsession with a fellow Transformers Fan, Ravette, for reasons which will forever remain a mystery. It started out harmlessly enough, stalking Ravette's page often and plagiarizing a little fanfic here and there, but after Ravette [[NO U|called her out on it]] in July, she began stalking in earnest. 

She was soon [[b&|blocked,]] but that did little to deter Bonita, as she continually checked her target's recent activity and left [[diarrhea|comments]] everywhere Ravette did. [[Krystal can't enjoy her sandwich|Ravette moved all her fanfiction]] to her own website to keep Bonita's [[bukkake|jizz-soaked hands]] off of it, but this was not enough to make her stop. 

Instead, a new, [[creepypasta|creepier]] phase of stalking ensued. [[Srsly|Every time]] Ravette mentioned something interesting about her life, Bonita copied it. When Ravette had an [[pain series|operation,]] Bonita mentioned having a [[fapping|trucking]] accident. When Ravette mentioned getting custom Transformers in the mail, suddenly [[This is why we can't have nice things|Bonita was ordering custom figures in the mail as well]]. 

Many people noticed this [[faggotry|habit]], and called Bonita out on her obsession. The resulting drama and wank spilled over to others' pages, most notably [http://raidenprime.deviantart.com raidenprime], where a strange and lulzacious proxy argument took place between raiden and [http://therealbumblebee.deviantart.com TheRealBumblebee].

